  "readingTitle": "evaluate — Paper 4 — Writing & translation into Spanish",
  "reading": "For top marks combine an opinion, a reason and a second tense in one sentence: ‘Me gusta la carne, pero voy a comer menos porque es mala para la salud.’ At Higher, add ‘se debería…’ or ‘aunque…’.",
  "question": "Which sentence would score highest?",
